the shell is done in 6 files
1.main.c
it is used for input formatting and small functions like pwd and echo are 
implemented in this itself
2.process.c
it contains background foreground and backhandler which checks the terminated 
background process
3.jobs.c
it contains functions related to linked list i created for storing jobs
4.prompt.c
it contains prompt function and functions related to fg bg and sig command
and standard output and input rediretion functions
5.sighan.c
it contains ctrlz and ctrlc handlers and jobs printing functions
6.cd.c
it contains cd related functions

